ered pieces tagged with rule-stack provenance, ablation tooling documented for operators, review log template in place. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ No newline at end of file\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ndiff --git a/sdp/run-log.md b/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nindex e10959b..082b4b0 100644\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n--- a/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+++ b/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -56,3 +56,19 @@\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n | run-t-008@20260416t054258z-1776353875 | T-008@20260416T054258Z | codex | gemini | PASS | 3723.7s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n | run-t-009@20260416t054258z-1776357613 | T-009@20260416T054258Z | codex | claude | PASS WITH NOTES | 608.3s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n | run-t-010@20260416t054258z-1776358237 | T-010@20260416T054258Z | claude | codex | PASS | 735.1s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-011@20260416t054258z-1776358988 | T-011@20260416T054258Z | gemini | claude | PASS WITH NOTES | 1556.3s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-012@20260416t054258z-1776360563 | T-012@20260416T054258Z | claude | gemini | PASS | 373.8s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-013@20260416t054258z-1776360951 | T-013@20260416T054258Z | codex | claude | PASS | 442.9s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-014@20260416t054258z-1776361411 | T-014@20260416T054258Z | claude | gemini | PASS | 490.9s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-015@20260416t054258z-1776361921 | T-015@20260416T054258Z | codex | claude | PASS | 667.7s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-016@20260416t054258z-1776362606 | T-016@20260416T054258Z | claude | gemini | PASS | 625.1s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-017@20260416t054258z-1776363251 | T-017@20260416T054258Z | codex | claude | — | 0.0s | — |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| run-t-017@2026